<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"><a href="https://kaspars.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/favourite-fvt-120a-12s-esc-skateboard-electric.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="3264" height="2448" src="https://kaspars.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/favourite-fvt-120a-12s-esc-skateboard-electric-800x600.jpg" alt="Favourite FVT 120A 12S ESC for Electric Skateboard" class="wp-image-6348" srcset="https://kaspars.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/favourite-fvt-120a-12s-esc-skateboard-electric-800x600.jpg 800w, https://kaspars.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/favourite-fvt-120a-12s-esc-skateboard-electric-1024x768.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3264px) 100vw, 3264px" /></a></figure></div>



